metadata.name: ☾𝚎𝚕𝚎𝚜𝚝𝚒𝚊𝚕 𝙷𝚘𝚛𝚒𝚣𝚘𝚗
metadata.description:
High above the clouds, where no birds fly
My dear angel plays on the Grand Wisdom piano. 
The notes tearing through the strings are resonating in my heart 
And I pray that you keep playing so that I don't feel lost.
